data.description: Immaculate two-story home in the exclusive Aberdeen community. Are you looking for a move-in ready home in a great school zone with plenty of space for your family? You found it! This Florida beauty has plenty of UPGRADES to offer:NEW FLOORS AND CARPET THROUGH OUT, VAULTED CEILINGS, GRAND MASTER SUITE, MASTER BATH INCLUDES DOUBLE VANITY AND REMARKABLE TILED STAND-UP SHOWER WITH SEPERATE OVERSIZED GARDEN TUB, SCREENED LANAI, plus more. Enjoy the Florida lifestyle by taking advantage of the many amenities offered by this prestigious community: Resort style pool, tennis courts, and fitness center. You have to see this home!
